comments: McDermott (SAS) reaches in and makes clean contact with the ball while defending Sabonis (SAC).
Bates-Diop (SAS) initiates contact across Sabonis's (SAC) arm, affecting his shot attempt near the rim.
Sabonis (SAC) briefly places two hands on Collins' (SAS) back in the post.
Sabonis (SAC) contests Collins's (SAS) post shot attempt and the contact after the release is marginal.

Champagnie (SAS) briefly places an arm to Murray's (SAC) front as the two players engage and move along the same path.  The contact is marginal and Murray is not dislodged from his defensive position as a result of the contact.
Sabonis (SAC) reaches in and marginal contact occurs as he grazes Champagnie's (SAS) hip during the driving shot attempt.
Collins (SAS) wraps and holds Sabonis (SAC), affecting his ability to pursue the rebound.
Murray (SAC) initiates contact with Barlow's (SAS) head during the layup attempt.
Branham (SAS) steps out of bounds at the start of his drive to the basket.
Branham (SAS) legally contests Huerter's (SAC) jump shot attempt.
